S4PA/Storage Version $Revision: 1.1.1.1 $ (S4PA $Name:  $)
=============================================

It contains methods for handling data compression, uncompression, checksum
computation, placing data in appropriate directories, creating symbolic links,
publication to WHOM, data delettion and granule record keeping.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

POSIX
Safe
File::Basename
File::stat
File::Copy
MLDBM
DB_File
Fcntl
S4P
S4P::TimeTools
S4PA::Receiving
XML::LibXML
XML::LibXML::NodeList
File::KGlob

